  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:1",
      "text": "本教程扩展了 Harsh Agrawal 在",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:2",
      "text": "Community Site version（社区网站版本）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:21",
      "text": "理解 PxrSurface 的基本设计。",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:23",
      "text": "PxrSurface",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:27",
      "text": "Specular（镜面反射）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:28",
      "text": "Rough Specular（粗糙镜面反射）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:29",
      "text": "Sub-Surface（次表面）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:33",
      "text": "Wikipedia",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:38",
      "text": "纹理应根据其目标效果和对象分配来恰当命名。例如：<object>_<effect>.jpg，或者 tableTop_specular.jpg。",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:39",
      "text": "不要在名称中使用空格和特殊字符，例如：theCar&boat.jpg 或 \"the Car and Boat.jpg\"。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:41",
      "text": "Texture sequences（纹理序列）应有清晰的帧号命名约定。mySequence.0001.jpg 是正确形式，而不是 mySequence0001.jpg 或 mySequence.jpg.0001。",
      "ascii_letters": 55,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:43",
      "text": ".tex format（.tex 格式）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:46",
      "text": "Diffuse 和 Albedo",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:47",
      "text": "Roughness 和 Glossiness（请注意，RenderMan 使用标准的 \"Roughness\" 约定，其中 0 = 镜面，1 = 粗糙或接近漫反射。）Roughness 也适用于 Diffuse 参数，因此艺术家有时会用 Glossiness 作为名称。",
      "ascii_letters": 63,
      "cjk_chars": 42
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:49",
      "text": "Normal maps 通常比 bump maps（scalar 或 grayscale）更适合用于表现细节。",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:50",
      "text": "Linear color workflow（线性色彩工作流）",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:55",
      "text": "进行 linearize（线性化）。",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:56",
      "text": "Displacement maps 和其他 data textures 应尽可能使用最高精度，以避免纹理量化造成的伪影。通常这些会从建模应用程序导出为 floating point EXR 或 Tiff。有关 normal 和 scalar displacement，请参见",
      "ascii_letters": 72,
      "cjk_chars": 47
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:57",
      "text": "workflows（工作流）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:59",
      "text": "如果 Maya File Node 具备你需要的功能，或者你喜欢使用 Maya workflow 处理 texture sequences 等内容的简洁性，那么没有特别理由不使用它进行纹理处理。Maya file node 和 PxrTexture node 都会在 viewport 中显示纹理。不过，只有 Maya file node 会在 viewport 中显示 UDIM/tiled textures，并对 viewport 应用校正后的 gamma。",
      "ascii_letters": 124,
      "cjk_chars": 70
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:60",
      "text": "Wood Table（木桌）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:70",
      "text": "通过 utility 节点传递贴图，以辅助 look development。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:74",
      "text": "pattern networks（模式网络）",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:78",
      "text": "Improving Performance（提升性能）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:83",
      "text": "下面，Specular Roughness 纹理通过一个",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:84",
      "text": "PxrColorCorrect",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:85",
      "text": "节点进行更改，并在 Maya 的 IPR 中调整。pattern 的 Color Correct 分区使用了不同的 Gamma 值。由于这张纹理是 grayscale（scalar）贴图，RGB 通道都具有相同的值。这里只操作 Red Channel，然后连接到 Primary Specular Roughness 参数。或者，也可以把 Color Correct pattern 连接到一个转换节点，例如",
      "ascii_letters": 102,
      "cjk_chars": 69
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:86",
      "text": "PxrToFloat",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:89",
      "text": "现在我们来看 Milk and Bottle。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:94",
      "text": "PxrLayerSurface",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:98",
      "text": "ray depth（射线深度）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:102",
      "text": "intersection priority（相交优先级）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:103",
      "text": "有助于避免伪影和 \"air gaps\"（空气间隙）。这在技术上称为 dielectric interface（电介质界面）或 nested dielectrics（嵌套电介质）。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:114",
      "text": "这里是使用的 mask，它在 PxrLayerMixer 中应用，用于全局控制 \"MilkDirt_Layer\"。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:127",
      "text": "displacement（位移）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:130",
      "text": "remap nodes 用于在渲染中调整 cookie 的 specular properties，如 Tray 分区中所述。",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:135",
      "text": "PxrDomeLight",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:137",
      "text": "PxrRectLight",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:138",
      "text": "的 rim light（轮廓光）和 key light（主光）。",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:140",
      "text": "emission focus（发射聚焦）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:142",
      "text": "Fill Light（补光）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:147",
      "text": "specular amount（镜面反射量）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:149",
      "text": "Rim Light（轮廓光）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:152",
      "text": "specular amount（镜面反射量）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2cef65d30e:154",
      "text": "Key Light（主光）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    }
  ],
